text: "OpenAI is an AGI research and deployment company. Our mission is to ensure that artificial general intelligence benefits all of humanity."

"OpenAI\u2019s large language models, including the models that power ChatGPT, are developed using three primary sources of information: (1) information that is publicly available on the internet, (2) information that we license from third parties, and (3) information that our users or our human trainers provide."
